<hymn_number>329</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka taksa lungkham mahlele,
 Van lam ah tha'n ka leng sek hi;
 Tuhin chauin mau mah le'ng le,
 Tunung leh tha'n hung leng ka ie.

[V2]
 Damlai ni a beih ma hin Lalpa,
 Hin kipahna him ka nei puoi;
 Kumsawt Zion khuo hungvak ta uo,
 Buoina chengcheng kipahna hung suok hen.

[V3]
 2. Gitloh a thi'n thim lak ahin,
 Kumsawt vak lam chu ka hawl a;
 Kei gimthei, chau leh sangawn hi,
 Nunnawpna'n ei hih bukim in.

[V4]
 3. Vang khawpi hawih Sana tuol nuom,
 Tung ta le'ng Pielgal khawpi chu,
 Nun lui gam hi vak thil ing ting,
 Ka kahna himhim ngai puo'ng ka.</lyrics>
<title>Zion Khuo Hungvak In</title>
</song>